title: Prénatal – zwangerschap en bab
description:
Are you pregnant? What an exciting time! You will be inundated with various advice and lots of information. Are you dizzy yet? In the free Prénatal app you will find answers to many of your questions. In the app you will find, among other things, a pregnancy calendar, a handy baby removal list and you will receive push notifications containing offers and tips.
Thanks to the pregnancy calendar, you will receive relevant information and interesting blog articles about your pregnancy every week. You can follow the development and growth of your little one; is he or she the size of a tomato or melon? With the countdown clock you can see how many weeks, hours and days it will take until your due date.
There is a lot to consider during pregnancy, delivery and the postpartum period. Now that you are pregnant you want to have everything arranged on time. That is why we have compiled a strike list for you from which you can easily shop and where you can tick what you already have at home. Handy, right?
And did you give birth? Even then we have relevant information for you! In our baby calendar you will find even more information about the development of your little one (s).
Finally; in the app you will always find our offers and thanks to our store locator you will always find a Prénatal store near you. No time to come to one of our stores? At home on the couch you can shop the things you need via www.prenatal.nl. Would you like to contact us? You will find all the ways you can reach us under one button in the app.
